Republican Nationalist Alliance, or Arena. He also was a member of a
Committee for the Rescue of the University of El Salvador, an
organization composed of former university professors and employees
who accuse the university of being a front for leftist rebels.
   On Friday, Rafael Mendez, a member of the same committee, came
under gunfire from attackers, but was unhurt.
   Mendez earlier in the day had complained to university officials
about what he said was the unjustified dismissal of university
employees. He also accused officials of being in league with the
rebels.
